import React from "react";


export const parentDivStyle: React.CSSProperties ={
    position: "relative",
    left:50,
    maxWidth: "100%",
    margin: "0 auto",
    backgroundSize: "cover",
    backgroundRepeat:"no-repeat",
    display: "flex",
    alignItems: "center",
    justifyContent: "center",
    height: "100vh",
}

export const loginButtonStyle: React.CSSProperties ={
    position: "relative",
    left:0,
    top:0
}
